About
-----
Hemera is a Virtual Intelligent System aggregating some more advanced Artificial Intelligence Technologies (speech, speech recognition, form recognition ...); with applications in day tasks, domotics and robotics ...

License
-------
Hemera is developed under the GNU General Public License version 3.0 (GPLv3).
See LICENSE or COPYING file.

Quick Start
-----------
 - to get speech samples
svn co https://hemerais.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/hemerais/trunk/Samples [HEMERA_ROOT_PATH]/HemeraSamples

Help
------------------
launch scripts/help.sh

